titles.title: A resolution congratulating the American College of Emergency Physicians on its 50th anniversary.
A resolution congratulating the American College of Emergency Physicians on its 50th anniversary.

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment and with a preamble by Unanimous Consent.

bill.summary: Congratulates the American College of Emergency Physicians on its 50th Anniversary. Recognizes the accomplishments and contributions emergency physicians have made to advance the health care system in the United States.
